# Ignore every top-level directory by default. This catches:
#   - every repo cloned from ade-repos.txt (no matter how the list evolves)
#   - workspace-local tooling dirs (.cursor/, .planning/ volatile bits, etc.)
#   - anything else that lands at the root
# Template-managed top-level FILES are unaffected by this pattern.
# See docs/DECISIONS.md D-014 for rationale.
/*/

# Allowlist .planning/ — it's template-managed (PROJECT.md + codebase/ intel).
!/.planning/

# Inside .planning/, GSD-volatile state is still ignored (per-project output).
/.planning/milestones/
/.planning/phases/
/.planning/intel/
/.planning/research/
/.planning/threads/
/.planning/state/
/.planning/config.json
/.planning/ROADMAP.md

# OS artifacts (can appear anywhere)
.DS_Store
